    <text id="A9514T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Pilson writes to McFarland of his inability to find a supply pastor for the next
                    week, as many are with the Army.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1863-08-12">Aug<hi rend="super">t</hi> 12<hi rend="super"
                            >th</hi> 1863</date>
                        <name type="place">Rocky Spring</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute><abbr expan="Reverend">Rev.</abbr> F. M<hi rend="super">c</hi>Farland DD
                        <lb/>My dear Friend </salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I was in Staunton yesterday and failed to get <abbr expan="Reverend">Rev.</abbr>
                    Mr <orig reg="Stuart">Stuard</orig> to preach on next <orig reg="Sabbath"
                    >Sabath</orig>, <abbr expan="Reverend">Rev.</abbr> Mr See had just <orig
                        reg="engaged">ingaged</orig> him for next <orig reg="Sabbath">Sabath</orig>,
                    he is going to the Army, I saw Mr Baker <orig reg="says">sayes</orig> it will
                        <orig reg="suit">suite</orig> him to be with us on Saturday and Sunday of
                    next week would like to be with his <orig reg="own">owen</orig> people on
                    Friday, that is the understanding unless we give him further notice, he says he
                    can come the next <orig reg="Sabbath">Sabath</orig> if that will <orig
                        reg="suit">suite</orig> us better, I did intend coming by your House on my
                    way home, but having to go by Fishersville in the morning and the day being so
                    very warm, I was unable to do so. In hopes you are improving.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I remain your sincere friend</salute>
                    <signed>Matthew Pilson</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
